<%= render "layouts/top", content_title: "Help", title: "How to Use Coupon Exchange", button_text: "Back To Dashboard", button_path: dashboards_path%>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6">
        
        <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">1. How It Works</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                <li>Sign up for an account and log in.</li>
                <li>Browse available coupons or list your unused coupons.</li>
                <li>Exchange coupons with other users securely.</li>
                <li>Redeem your coupons at participating stores.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6 mt-4">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <details class="mb-4 border-b pb-2">
                <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold">Is the platform free to use?</summary>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">Yes, signing up and exchanging coupons is completely free.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="mb-4 border-b pb-2">
                <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold">How do I list a coupon?</summary>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">Go to your dashboard and click 'Add Coupon', fill in the details, and publish it.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
                <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold">How do I contact support?</summary>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">You can reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@couponexchange.com" class="text-blue-600">support@couponexchange.com</a>.</p>
            </details>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6 mt-4">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Need More Help?</h2>
            <p>If you have any other questions, feel free to contact our support team. We're here to help!</p>
            <a href="mailto:support@couponexchange.com" class="font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500 hover:underline">Contact Support</a>
        </div>
    </div>